data.description: The Sellers has decreased the price to sell. Cute and cozy home with a Fireplace, Fresh paint and New carpet. Great for a starter home or investment. Granite countertop with a breakfast bar and matching backsplash. Kitchen and restrooms are tiled. Shed in the yard can be a Man Cave, She Shed or a storage. Owner had a few fruit trees that now needs some TLC. Home has some good features and has strong bones. Home has a fence-in backyard and also an attached patio that needs a little TLC. Owner is anxious to sell. Home is less 5 mins to I-59 and 7-10 mins to the Deer Brooks Mall, Shops and Restaurants.  Also, Intercontinental Airport 15-20 mins away or 20 mins to Downtown Houston.
